  "8": {"a":{"g":"Allah does not forbid you from those who do not fight you because of religion and do not expel you from your homes - from being righteous toward them and acting justly toward them. Indeed, Allah loves those who act justly."},"w":[{"b":"0.08","c":"لَّا","d":"lā","e":"Not","h":"0.26"},{"b":"0.51","c":"يَنۡهَىٰكُمُ","d":"yanhākumu","e":"(does) forbid you","h":"0.7"},{"b":"1.8","c":"ٱللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"Allah","h":"2.14"},{"b":"2.3","c":"عَنِ","d":"ʿani","e":"from","h":"2.87"},{"b":"2.8","c":"ٱلَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"those who","h":"3.34"},{"b":"3.8","c":"لَمۡ","d":"lam","e":"(do) not","h":"4.43"},{"b":"4.1","c":"يُقَٰتِلُوكُمۡ","d":"yuqātilūkum","e":"fight you","h":"4.7"},{"b":"5.7","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","h":"6.63"},{"b":"6","c":"ٱلدِّينِ","d":"l-dīni","e":"the religion","h":"6.98"},{"b":"6.7","c":"وَلَمۡ","d":"walam","e":"and (do) not","h":"7.9"},{"b":"7.3","c":"يُخۡرِجُوكُم","d":"yukh'rijūkum","e":"drive you out","h":"8.39"},{"b":"9.8","c":"مِّن","d":"min","e":"of","h":"10.6"},{"b":"10.6","c":"دِيَٰرِكُمۡ","d":"diyārikum","e":"your homes","h":"11.42"},{"b":"11.7","c":"أَن","d":"an","e":"that","h":"12.78"},{"b":"12.8","c":"تَبَرُّوهُمۡ","d":"tabarrūhum","e":"you deal kindly","h":"13.61"},{"b":"14.2","c":"وَتُقۡسِطُوٓاْ","d":"watuq'siṭū","e":"and deal justly","h":"15.29"},{"b":"16.7","c":"إِلَيۡهِمۡۚ","d":"ilayhim","e":"with them","h":"17.89"},{"b":"18.1","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"Indeed","h":"20.85"},{"b":"19.4","c":"ٱللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"Allah","h":"21.99"},{"b":"20.2","c":"يُحِبُّ","d":"yuḥibbu","e":"loves","h":"22.85"},{"b":"21.0","c":"ٱلۡمُقۡسِطِينَ","d":"l-muq'siṭīna","e":"those who act justly","h":"23.83"}]},
  "9": {"a":{"g":"Allah only forbids you from those who fight you because of religion and expel you from your homes and aid in your expulsion - [forbids] that you make allies of them. And whoever makes allies of them, then it is those who are the wrongdoers."},"w":[{"b":"0.15","c":"إِنَّمَا","d":"innamā","e":"Only","h":"0.75"},{"b":"1.7","c":"يَنۡهَىٰكُمُ","d":"yanhākumu","e":"forbids you","h":"2.23"},{"b":"2.9","c":"ٱللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"Allah","h":"3.77"},{"b":"3.6","c":"عَنِ","d":"ʿani","e":"from","h":"4.46"},{"b":"4.0","c":"ٱلَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"those who","h":"4.99"},{"b":"5.0","c":"قَٰتَلُوكُمۡ","d":"qātalūkum","e":"fight you","h":"6.07"},{"b":"6.4","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","h":"7.59"},{"b":"6.7","c":"ٱلدِّينِ","d":"l-dīni","e":"the religion","h":"7.91"},{"b":"7.4","c":"وَأَخۡرَجُوكُم","d":"wa-akhrajūkum","e":"and drive you out","h":"8.81"},{"b":"8.6","c":"مِّن","d":"min","e":"of","h":"11.16"},{"b":"10.4","c":"دِيَٰرِكُمۡ","d":"diyārikum","e":"your homes","h":"12.05"},{"b":"11.","c":"وَظَٰهَرُواْ","d":"waẓāharū","e":"and support","h":"13.31"},{"b":"12.7","c":"عَلَىٰٓ","d":"ʿalā","e":"in","h":"14.85"},{"b":"13.0","c":"إِخۡرَاجِكُمۡ","d":"ikh'rājikum","e":"your expulsion","h":"16.39"},{"b":"15.8","c":"أَن","d":"an","e":"that","h":"18.11"},{"b":"17.0","c":"تَوَلَّوۡهُمۡۚ","d":"tawallawhum","e":"you make them allies","h":"19.11"},{"b":"19","c":"وَمَن","d":"waman","e":"And whoever","h":"23.73"},{"b":"20.3","c":"يَتَوَلَّهُمۡ","d":"yatawallahum","e":"makes them allies","h":"24.93"},{"b":"21.5","c":"فَأُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ","d":"fa-ulāika","e":"then those","h":"26.39"},{"b":"24.","c":"هُمُ","d":"humu","e":"[they]","h":"29.15"},{"b":"24.6","c":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمُونَ","d":"l-ẓālimūna","e":"(are) the wrongdoers","h":"29.7"}]},
  "10": {"a":{"g":"O you who have believed, when the believing women come to you as emigrants, examine them. Allah is most knowing as to their faith. And if you know them to be believers, then do not return them to the disbelievers; they are not lawful [wives] for them, nor are they lawful [husbands] for them. But give the disbelievers what they have spent. And there is no blame upon you if you marry them when you have given them their due compensation. And hold not to marriage bonds with disbelieving women, but ask for what you have spent and let them ask for what they have spent. That is the judgement of Allah; He judges between you. And Allah is Knowing and Wise."},"w":[{"b":"0.2","c":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","d":"yāayyuhā","e":"O you","h":"1.93"},{"b":"2.8","c":"ٱلَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"who","h":"2.9"},{"b":"3.8","c":"ءَامَنُوٓاْ","d":"āmanū","e":"believe","h":"4.03"},{"b":"6.4","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"When","h":"4.89"},{"b":"7.0","c":"جَآءَكُمُ","d":"jāakumu","e":"come to you","h":"6.93"},{"b":"9.5","c":"ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتُ","d":"l-mu'minātu","e":"the believing women","h":"8.8"},{"b":"10.8","c":"مُهَٰجِرَٰتٖ","d":"muhājirātin","e":"(as) emigrants","h":"10.32"},{"b":"12.9","c":"فَٱمۡتَحِنُوهُنَّۖ","d":"fa-im'taḥinūhunna","e":"then examine them","h":"12.74"},{"b":"16.1","c":"ٱللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"Allah","h":"18.15"},{"b":"16.9","c":"أَعۡلَمُ","d":"aʿlamu","e":"(is) most knowing","h":"19.1"},{"b":"17.6","c":"بِإِيمَٰنِهِنَّۖ","d":"biīmānihinna","e":"of their faith","h":"20.09"},{"b":"20.","c":"فَإِنۡ","d":"fa-in","e":"And if","h":"25.05"},{"b":"20.9","c":"عَلِمۡتُمُوهُنَّ","d":"ʿalim'tumūhunna","e":"you know them","h":"25.59"},{"b":"23.","c":"مُؤۡمِنَٰتٖ","d":"mu'minātin","e":"(to be) believers","h":"28.2"},{"b":"25.4","c":"فَلَا","d":"falā","e":"then (do) not","h":"30.43"},{"b":"26.0","c":"تَرۡجِعُوهُنَّ","d":"tarjiʿūhunna","e":"return them","h":"31.22"},{"b":"28.1","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"to","h":"33.79"},{"b":"28.4","c":"ٱلۡكُفَّارِۖ","d":"l-kufāri","e":"